<p>I have the following case where I want to return the <code>sharedInstance</code> of <code>MySubclass</code></p>  <pre><code>class MySingleton {     static let sharedInstance = MySingleton()       ....  } </code></pre>  <p><br/></p>  <pre><code>class MySubclass:MySingleton {     .... } </code></pre>  <p><code>MySubclass.sharedInstance</code> returns a <code>MySingleton</code> not a <code>MySubclass</code>.</p>  <p>Any idea how to achieve that ? </p>